  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>Animation trimming: Manual and pose-matched options.</li><li>Root bone modification. <strong>Lock</strong>: force multiple frames to inherit the translation/rotation of the root bone at a specified frame. <strong>Constrain</strong>: give the root bone another bone&#39;s ground-projected position/rotation. <strong>Align with axis</strong>: aligns the root trajectory with a direction specified by given a locomotion angle. <strong>Trajectory smoothing</strong>: moving average, linear interp, or Savitzky-Golay.</li><li>Offset removal</li><li>Curve generation for root motion: Distance (Paragon/Lyra style), speed, velocity, and acceleration. Derivative-based curves can use either the finite-difference or Savitzky-Golay method of differentiation.</li><li>Animation-end blending: match the first and last pose of an animation to the same or another animation&#39;s first/last pose.</li><li>IK-to-FK bone constraint.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Code Modules:</p><ul><li> MotionCaptureTools (Editor)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 0</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 18</p><p>Network Replicated: N/A. This plugin is editor-only.</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Win64</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64</p><p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OVx8H7VGQ1_XdaPFxRNlVYDktbdolx7KWTXBbxJLyac/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation</a>: Join <a href=\"https://discord.gg/se24X9c2Dc\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord</a> for direct support.</p>",
